name: FRigVMGraphParameterDescription
doc:
The parameter description is used to convey information
about unique parameters within a Graph. Multiple Parameter
Nodes can share the same parameter description.

Name: FName
The name of the parameter
bIsInput: True if the parameter is an input
CPPType: The C++ data type of the parameter
CPPTypeObject: The Struct of the C++ data type of the parameter (or nullptr)
DefaultValue: The default value of the parameter
